Germany’s Schaeuble Says Euro-Area Situation ’Serious’

-- B y   S t e p h a n i e   B o d o n i
-- 
2011-10-21T11:51:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/germany-s-schaeuble-says-euro-area-situation-serious-.html
German Finance Minister  Wolfgang
Schaeuble  said the situation in the euro area is “serious.”  “The situation is serious and we have a great
responsibility, everyone knows that,” Schaeuble told reporters
today in Brussels.  To contact the reporter on this story:
